{"tid":2231654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"侵侵：選民登記大炒民主黨","createTime":"2020-10-05T22:25:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T17:19:12.000Z","uid":270220,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"19aaaa0df307a5b56c3c8b7494afda6eaa66a1d7","tid":2231654,"uid":270220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T22:25:03.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;You see it in enthusiasm for the President outside Walter Reed Hospital. You see it in Registrations, from Florida to Pennsylvania &amp; West Virginia, where Republicans are outstripping Democrats by 2 to 1. If the President bounces back onto the campaign trail, he will be a invincible hero, who not only survived every dirty trick the Democrats threw at him, but the Chinese virus as well. He will show America we no longer have to be afraid.&rdquo; mdevine@nypost.com  Thank you Miranda. Was over until the Plague came in from China. Will win anyway!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realdonaldtrump/status/1313236039725649927?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frealdonaldtrump%2Fstatus%2F1313236039725649927%3Fs%3D21&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZLy%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=929da001\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frealdonaldtrump%2Fstatus%2F1313236039725649927%3Fs%3D21&h=e310f2a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realdonaldtrump/status/1313236039725649927?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPresident Trump is winning the voter registration battle against Joe Biden in key states.<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/nbcnews/status/1311688583951069186?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnbcnews%2Fstatus%2F1311688583951069186%3Fs%3D21&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZLy%2F0jIrp0bHqVoz25JuQVd4%3D&h=e7c948a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnbcnews%2Fstatus%2F1311688583951069186%3Fs%3D21&h=28f63ffa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/nbcnews/status/1311688583951069186?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"86da7153a99c153c2b84a8ab2c2820fd04b6f30a","tid":2231654,"uid":270220,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T22:28:04.000Z","msg":"In Florida, Republicans added a net 195,652 registered voters between this March's presidential primary and the end of August, while Democrats added 98,362 and other voters increased 69,848.<br />\n<br />\nIn Pennsylvania, Republicans added a net 135,619 voters between this June's primary and the final week of September, while Democrats added 57,985 and other voters increased 49,995<br />\n<br />\nIn North Carolina, Republicans added a net 83,785 voters between this March's presidential primary and the final week of September, while Democrats added 38,137 and other voters jumped 100,256.<br />\n<br />\nIn Arizona, Democrats out-registered Republicans 31,139 to 29,667 on a net basis between the March presidential primary and the August state primary, compared to Democrats topping Republicans 66,523 to 53,185 over the same period in 2016.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1b7e2cecd89185faf2fed0e32084f60e2757ac","tid":2231654,"uid":155095,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T22:28:16.000Z","msg":"不過拜登有華人、黑人、同其他少數族裔一面倒支持，sure win啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f952907648b0f6b5ea12fa6eb0f9c8b8245b6931","tid":2231654,"uid":270220,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"de1b7e2cecd89185faf2fed0e32084f60e2757ac","tid":2231654,"uid":15509